Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:07.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Thread by thread, stitching it together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:11.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Twilight's dress, cutting out the pattern snip by snip
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Making sure the fabric folds nicely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect color and so hip
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Always got to keep in mind my pacing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Making sure the cloth's correctly facing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:24.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm stitching Twilight's dress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:30.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yard by yard, fussing on the details
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Jewel neckline
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't you know a stitch in time saves nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:36.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Make her something perfect to inspire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even though she hates formal attire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Gotta mind those intimate details
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:42.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even though she's more concerned with sales
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:47.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's Applejack's new dress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Dressmaking's easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:53.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For Pinkie Pie something pink
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy something breezy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:56.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Blend color and form
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do you think it looks cheesy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:05.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Something brash, perhaps quite fetching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:09.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hook and eye, couldn't you just simply DIE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Making sure it fits forelock and crest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't forget some magic in the dress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even though it rides high on the flank
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:17.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Rainbow won't look like a tank
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:23.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm stitching Rainbow's dress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:26.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, snip by snip
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:28.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Croup, dock, haunch, shoulders, hip
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Thread by thread, primmed and pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:33.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yard by yard, never stressed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:39.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And that's the art of the dress~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:43.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now, the stars on my belt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:44.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Need to be technically accurate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Orion has three stars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:48.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,On his belt, not four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Stitch by stitch, stitching it together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:54.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Deadline looms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:57.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't you know the client's always right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even if my fabric choice was perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Gotta get them all done by tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, the color's too obtrusive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Wait until you see it in the light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:09.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm sewing them together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:10.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't you think my gown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Would be more me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With some lollipops?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:13.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Balloons?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:14.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:15.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:19.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hour by hour, one more change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:23.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm sewing them together, take great pains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you're putting me in a bind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, what is on your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, there's simply not much time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, Applejack's duds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:36.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Must shi-i-ine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Dressmaking's easy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:39.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every customer's call
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Brings a whole new revision
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Have to pick up the pace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Still hold to my vision
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That constellation is Canis Major, not Minor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,French haute couture, please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Eeeh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:58.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What if it rains? Galoshes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,More balloons! Oh no, that's too many balloons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,More candy! Oh, less candy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, I know! Streamers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Streamers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Whose dress is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Streamers it is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:15.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To change something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:18.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, I just want
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My dress to be... cool
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do you not like the color?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The color's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just make it look cooler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Do you not like the shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The shape's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:27.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just make the whole thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:29.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You know, cooler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It needs to be about 20% cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we ever want is indecision
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:37.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All we really like is what we know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Gotta balance style with adherence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Making sure we make a good appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even if you simply have to fudge it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Make sure that it stays within our budget
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Got to overcome intimidation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:51.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Remember it's all in the presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, snip by snip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Croup, dock, haunch, shoulders, hip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Bolt by bolt, primmed and pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yard by yard, always stressed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:06.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And that's the art of the dress